Files in this directory:

	links.dat	A RcdFile. The database of links. This file is
			edited by curators as needed.

	install		To be called by mgihome installer. Defined
			MGIHOME variable and adds unique keys to
			link records. Reads links.dat, writes .links.

	.links		A RcdFile. The file written by install, and
			the one actually read by getLinks.cgi. 

	getLinks.cgi	Python CGI script. This is the script that
			provides query access to the database of links.
			Used by CGIs in the wi to add links to detail pages.

	qf.html		A simple query form for testing getLinks.cgi.
			
